<br>
I think someone had established that No_Drop items had a &quot;ghost flag&quot;.  In other words, the No_Drop flag is still on the item, invisible and turned off but still present.  That's what causes items like the Microprocessors and the Gnoll Teeth to &quot;nerf&quot;.<br>
<br>
All the items I've seen disappear due to the Trivial Loot Code have been originally No_Drop items: the Orc Runner's head, Gnoll Teeth, Microprocessors.  I'm still fairly low level and inexperienced, so your results may vary.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
